AnnieMurphyPaul_2011G 1 AnnieMurphyPaul_2011G 444.76 457.16 <o,f0,female> through one of culture 's most powerful expressions which is food they 're being introduced to the characteristic flavors and spices of their culture 's cuisine even before birth
AnnieMurphyPaul_2011G 1 AnnieMurphyPaul_2011G 457.16 466.3 <o,f0,female> now it turns out that fetuses are learning even bigger lessons but before i get to that i want to address something that you may be wondering about
